How I Attach Bundles To A Sleek Ponytail!!!!!

✨Step By Step Instructions✨

1. Sew Bundles Starting At The Bottom Of The Client’s Braid & Work Your away Up To The Base Of The Ponytail! (Wrap Twice & Then Sew)
2. Take A Piece Of Hair From Under The Ponytail, Spray Holding Spray On Piece & Smooth Upward With Rat Tail Comb. Begin Wrapping Around The Base Of The Ponytail. (Repeat Steps Until There’s No More Hair To Wrap Around.
3. Spray Wrap Around One More Time & Blow Dry On Low Heat To Lock In Wrap Around.
4. Style Loose Hair In Desired Style!

If Interested In 1-On-1 Ponytail Class, Please Feel Free To Contact Me!
